  "description": "Unknown woods is a brutal FPS game where missing a shot can mean life or death\nYou are a man who is obsessed with mythical creatures of the woods and you are on an adventure to a closed of and banned to the public area of the forest. In here you are trying to find out if the legends are true and do the mythical creatures actually exist.\n\nFeatures:\n\n Two Hand crafted semi open worlds.\n\nTen different locations to explore.\n\nDifferent paths to achieve the goals.\n\nMythical creatures and aggressive wildlife to fight.\n\nBrutal damage, missing a shot can be fatal.\n\nDark and creepy atmosphere\n\nNo Saving\n\nNVIDIA DLSS support",
  "description_short": "A brutal horror action FPS where you will be fighting for survival against creatures of the woods and finding out the mysteries that lie around in the dark forest",
